 Kubrick, Ritchie and Soderbergh), are so drawn to this popular genre.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aCaper filmsxHistory and criticism. 0aCrime filmsxHistory and criticism. 0aDetective and mystery filmsxHistory and criticism. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertColumbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311066586440uhttps://doi.org/10.7312/lee-1696940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780231850582423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780231850582.jpg  a978-3-11-066586-4  Columbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles